org.apache.flex.compiler.definitions

Interface IMetadataDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDefinition, IDocumentableDefinition
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IEffectDefinition, IEventDefinition, IStyleDefinition
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EffectDefinition, EventDefinition, MetadataDefinitionBase, StyleDefinition

    public interface IMetadataDefinition
extends IDocumentableDefinition
    This interface represents definition which are themselves defined by metadata, such as definitions for events, styles, and effects.
